Class ResearcherLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.genologics.ri.researcher.ResearcherLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LimsLink<Researcher>, Linkable<Researcher>, Locatable, Serializable

    public class ResearcherLink
extends Object
implements LimsLink<Researcher>, Serializable
    Researcher-link is a child element type of researchers and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of a researcher.
